rComments: The course was useless. Nothing learnt from someone reading notes all along. Besides, he's r-acist. He's hard with foreigners and immigrants students and very generous with the others when it comes to grades.

A course on Teaching and Evaluation that taught us neither! This prof preached diversification of teaching strategies yet did nothing but lecture one class after the next on theory and psychology.  To top it off, assignments were consistently confusing and far from practical.

He was all over the map.  Nothing was clear.  This was suppose to be a class about how to properly manage class evaluations in High School and his tests and assignments were in no way succesful in demonstrating how we as future teachers should conduct proper evaluations.  Way to psychological.  Stay on Earth buddy.
